(324282, 'Earthshock, Part One', 766, '<p>The Doctor lands the Tardis in an underground cavern on 26th century Earth. Then the Doctor, Tegan, Nyssa and Adric become embroiled in the search for a team of missing scientists being preformed by the military.</p>', 19, 19, '1982-03-08', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/105349.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324282/doctor-who-19x19-earthshock-part-one'),
(324283, 'Earthshock, Part Two', 766, '<p>The Doctor discovers a bomb planted by the Cybermen, disarms it and then materializes the Tardis onto a freighter orbiting the Earth where mysterious murders are also being committed.</p>', 20, 19, '1982-03-09', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/105365.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324283/doctor-who-19x20-earthshock-part-two'),
(324284, 'Earthshock, Part Three', 766, '<p>Captain Briggs takes the Doctor prisoner, suspecting him of being behind the murders on board. Meanwhile the Cybermen start the process of taking over the ship with the help of a traitorous crew member. The Cybermen also start reviving other Cybermen who are hidden away as cargo.</p>', 21, 19, '1982-03-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/105402.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324284/doctor-who-19x21-earthshock-part-three'),
(324285, 'Earthshock, Part Four', 766, '<p>The Cybermen have taken over the bridge of the freighter. They fit a device onto the freighters control panel that will cause the ship to explode. The ships fuel will cause a explosion so strong that it will destroy the Earth completely. The Doctor and Companions battle against the Cybermen in an attempt to foil their plan. Someone pays the ultimate price to save the Earth and crew of the freighter.</p>', 22, 19, '1982-03-16', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/105431.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324285/doctor-who-19x22-earthshock-part-four'),
(324286, 'Time-Flight, Part One', 766, '<p>The Doctor still dealing with Adric''s death, lands the Tardis at London''s Heathrow airport and soon becomes involved with a missing Concord SST.</p>', 23, 19, '1982-03-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/105834.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324286/doctor-who-19x23-time-flight-part-one'),
(324287, 'Time-Flight, Part Two', 766, '<p>The Doctor''s Tardis vanishes, while tracking it down the Doctor encounters a strange being named "Kalid" who seems to be in control of events.</p>', 24, 19, '1982-03-23', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/105838.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324287/doctor-who-19x24-time-flight-part-two'),
(324288, 'Time-Flight, Part Three', 766, '<p>The Master commandeers the Doctors Tardis, leaving the Doctor behind to figure out what the alien artifact is.</p>', 25, 19, '1982-03-29', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/105843.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324288/doctor-who-19x25-time-flight-part-three'),
(324289, 'Time-Flight, Part Four', 766, '<p>The Doctor partially works with The Master, the crew of the Concord jury rig the plane so they can take off with the Doctor''s help. The Doctor follows The Master back to Heathrow airport. The Doctor announces that the temporal limiter The Master conned him out of will need replacing and that he is going to be stuck. Tegan gets accidentally left behind at Heathrow.</p>', 26, 19, '1982-03-30', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/105844.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324289/doctor-who-19x26-time-flight-part-four'),
(324291, 'Arc of Infinity, Part One', 766, '<p>On Gallifrey, someone commits a treasonous act and transmits the Doctor''s bio-extract from The Matrix to a unknown being. Meanwhile on Earth, two students spend the night in a underground crypt in Amsterdam and are attacked by a alien creature.</p>', 1, 20, '1983-01-04', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/105863.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324291/doctor-who-20x01-arc-of-infinity-part-one'),
(324292, 'Arc of Infinity, Part Two', 766, '<p>With a anti-matter being trying to enter the universe through the Doctor, the Gallifreyan high council see''s only one clear course of action. They decided to put the Doctor to death in order to prevent the occurrence.</p>', 2, 20, '1983-01-05', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/105869.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324292/doctor-who-20x02-arc-of-infinity-part-two'),
(324293, 'Arc of Infinity, Part Three', 766, '<p>The Council follows through with their death order and Omega holds the Doctor in Limbo. Commander Maxil discover''s that Nyssa was right and the Doctors Bio-Extract had been transmitted from The Matrix.Tegan finds her cousin who is under alien control.</p>', 3, 20, '1983-01-11', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/105871.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324293/doctor-who-20x03-arc-of-infinity-part-three'),
(324294, 'Arc of Infinity, Part Four', 766, '<p>The Doctor having returned to Earth, finds Omega''s Tardis and is not able to prevent Omega''s transfer upon arrival. Omega being of anti-matter and unstable is on the verge of destroying the planet in his attempt to regain a body.</p>', 4, 20, '1983-01-12', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/105888.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324294/doctor-who-20x04-arc-of-infinity-part-four'),
(324295, 'Snakedance, Part One', 766, '<p>The Tardis lands on the home world of the Sumaran civilization. The Doctor did not set the co-ordinates for the landing and discovers that Tegan did. He starts questioning if the Mara is still active inside of her from their previous adventure on the Kinda world.</p>', 5, 20, '1983-01-18', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/105901.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324295/doctor-who-20x05-snakedance-part-one'),
(324296, 'Snakedance, Part Two', 766, '<p>The Doctor finds out about the legend of the Mara''s return. Tegan goes into the cave and see''s a Mara skull in one of the mirrors. Tegan summons Lon to her.</p>', 6, 20, '1983-01-19', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/105909.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324296/doctor-who-20x06-snakedance-part-two'),
(324297, 'Snakedance, Part Three', 766, '<p>Possessed Tegan and Lon try to find the location of the Great Crystal. The Doctor finds himself in prison with only Nyssa to get him out while Chela tells the Doctor about Dojjen and gives him Dojjen''s journal.</p>', 7, 20, '1983-01-25', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/105914.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324297/doctor-who-20x07-snakedance-part-three'),
(324298, 'Snakedance, Part Four', 766, '<p>The Mara''s plan is close to fruition, the Doctor comes to prevent the Mara from finalizing the plan with the knowledge that Dojjen imparted to him.</p>', 8, 20, '1983-01-26', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/105918.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324298/doctor-who-20x08-snakedance-part-four'),
(324299, 'Mawdryn Undead, Part One', 766, '<p>The Black Guardian strikes a deal with a school student named Turlough to kill the Doctor. He promises him that he will take him back to his home planet if he does the job. Meanwhile The Doctor''s Tardis is trapped by a hidden device near Turlough''s school.</p>', 9, 20, '1983-02-01', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/106747.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324299/doctor-who-20x09-mawdryn-undead-part-one'),
(324300, 'Mawdryn Undead, Part Two', 766, '<p>The Doctor is stranded on Earth in 1983 while Tegan and Nyssa are looking for him in 1977. Tegan and Nyssa encounter a injured man they believe to be the doctor. Both the Doctor And Tegan and Nyssa encounter Brigadier Lethbridge Stewart who seems to have no memory of The Doctor.</p>', 10, 20, '1983-02-02', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/106748.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324300/doctor-who-20x10-mawdryn-undead-part-two'),
(324301, 'Mawdryn Undead, Part Three', 766, '<p>The Doctor travels to the orbiting spaceship with the Brigadier. Soon to discover a piece of Timelord technology on board the ship. Tegan and Turlough travel to the ship with their version of the Brigadier.</p>', 11, 20, '1983-02-08', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/106750.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324301/doctor-who-20x11-mawdryn-undead-part-three'),
(324302, 'Mawdryn Undead, Part Four', 766, '<p>The Doctor is on the ship and his future looks bleak as he is about to loose all his Timelord abilities to the Mawdryn. Both the Brigadier''s come in to the Mawdryns room with the Timelord artifact right as the transfer is starting.</p>', 12, 20, '1983-02-09', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/106751.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324302/doctor-who-20x12-mawdryn-undead-part-four'),
(324303, 'Terminus, Part One', 766, '<p>Turlough sabotages the Tardis under the Black Guardian''s direction and the Tardis materializes in the nearest ship. Nyssa is trapped in her room and has to escape into the spaceship the Tardis''s emergency circuits have landed it on.</p>', 13, 20, '1983-02-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/106758.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324303/doctor-who-20x13-terminus-part-one'),
(324304, 'Terminus, Part Two', 766, '<p>The two people the Doctor meets who have broken into the ship realize that they are on Terminus, where people who have the Lazar disease are sent to die. The Doctor finds it strange that the ship is at the exact center of the universe.</p>', 14, 20, '1983-02-16', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/106760.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324304/doctor-who-20x14-terminus-part-two'),
(324305, 'Terminus, Part Three', 766, '<p>The guards think the Doctor and those with him are investigators since they are not Lazars and are armed. Nyssa is taken off to be treated for the disease by the Garm.</p>', 15, 20, '1983-02-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/106761.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324305/doctor-who-20x15-terminus-part-three'),
(324306, 'Terminus, Part Four', 766, '<p>The Doctor discovers that the pilot had dumped the ships fuel billions of years ago and that the ship is going into another automatic fuel dump sequence because of the damaged engine. He determines that if the fuel gets dumped into space again, it will cause the destruction of the universe. Nyssa makes a decision that affects everyone.</p>', 16, 20, '1983-02-23', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/106759.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324306/doctor-who-20x16-terminus-part-four'),
(324307, 'Enlightenment, Part One', 766, '<p>The Doctor receives a warning from the White Guardian and is given co-ordinates to materialize the Tardis at. He lands the Tardis on a ship Captained by one of the Eternals. A Clairvoyant race that never dies and plays games involving mortals to relieve their boredom.</p>', 17, 20, '1983-03-01', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/106775.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324307/doctor-who-20x17-enlightenment-part-one'),
(324308, 'Enlightenment, Part Two', 766, '<p>Captain Striker reveals to the Doctor that they are Eternal''s and that they use ephemeral beings. The Black Guardian gets harsher with Turlough. The Captain takes the Tardis away from the Doctor.</p>', 18, 20, '1983-03-02', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/106779.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324308/doctor-who-20x18-enlightenment-part-two'),
(324309, 'Enlightenment, Part Three', 766, '<p>Captain Wrack rescues Turlough and see''s his coming aboard as a opportunity to invite all the other Captains over and use their visit to her advantage.</p>', 19, 20, '1983-03-08', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/106871.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324309/doctor-who-20x19-enlightenment-part-three'),
(324310, 'Enlightenment, Part Four', 766, '<p>Captain Wrack sets Tegan up to destroy Striker and his ship without her knowing it. Tegan convinces Captain Wrack to send the Doctor back to Striker''s ship where the Doctor works to foil her plot and defeat the Black Guardian.</p>', 20, 20, '1983-03-09', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/106880.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324310/doctor-who-20x20-enlightenment-part-four'),
(324311, 'The King''s Demons, Part One', 766, '<p>The Doctor lands the Tardis in 1215 England at the Castle of Ranulf Fitzwilliam in the middle of a jousting tournament and the Doctor is immediately hailed as a demon by the king. The Doctor finds this very suspicious. SPOILER ALERT: If you are watching this episode for the first time, wait until it is over to view the main cast as that will give some of the plot away.</p>', 21, 20, '1983-03-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/44/111805.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324311/doctor-who-20x21-the-kings-demons-part-one'),
(324312, 'The King''s Demons, Part Two', 766, '<p>The Doctor having discovered that The Master is behind the false King, works to stop the Master from preventing the Magna Carta to be signed.</p>', 22, 20, '1983-03-16', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/44/111808.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324312/doctor-who-20x22-the-kings-demons-part-two'),
(324314, 'Warriors of the Deep, Part One', 766, '<p>The Doctor materializes the TARDIS inside a underwater military base in 2084 during wartime. The base is about to be attacked on two fronts, secret agents within and a unknown enemy outside of the base.</p>', 1, 21, '1984-01-05', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/46/115872.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324314/doctor-who-21x01-warriors-of-the-deep-part-one'),
(324315, 'Warriors of the Deep, Part Two', 766, '<p>Just as the doctor is starting to gain a tentative trust from the humans of the underwater military base, an unknown cruiser appears and the Doctor seems to recognize it and warns the humans not to fire upon it.</p>', 2, 21, '1984-01-06', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/46/115894.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324315/doctor-who-21x02-warriors-of-the-deep-part-two'),
(324316, 'Warriors of the Deep, Part Three', 766, '<p>While the Silurians and Sea Devils attack the bases air locks, the saboteurs take advantage of the distraction to go ahead with their own plans.</p><p></p>', 3, 21, '1984-01-12', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/46/115895.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324316/doctor-who-21x03-warriors-of-the-deep-part-three'),
(324317, 'Warriors of the Deep, Part Four', 766, '<p>The Doctor is presented with a moral dilemma when Icthar reveals his plans to get rid of the human race so the Silurians can take back what was once theirs.</p>', 4, 21, '1984-01-13', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/46/115897.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324317/doctor-who-21x04-warriors-of-the-deep-part-four'),
(324330, 'The Awakening, Part One', 766, '<p>The TARDIS arrives in Little Hodcombe, Tegan wants to visit her Grandfather while they are there. Also, a war re-enactment is going on that starts to get more and more out of hand and realistic for unknown reasons.</p>', 5, 21, '1984-01-19', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/46/116969.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324330/doctor-who-21x05-the-awakening-part-one'),
(324331, 'The Awakening, Part Two', 766, '<p>The Malus is forcing the towns people to preform the re-enactment for real as it needs the psychic forces created by the suffering of war to feed off of and recharge it''s energies. It is up to the Doctor to prevent the Malus plans from reaching fruition.</p>', 6, 21, '1984-01-20', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/46/116970.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324331/doctor-who-21x06-the-awakening-part-two'),
(324332, 'Frontios, Part One', 766, '<p>In the far distant future, the few remaining survivors of the human race struggle to survive on the planet Frontios. The Doctor states that the Laws of time do not allow him to have contact because the survivors must go their own way without outside intervention at this key point in time.A meteor storm hits the planet and starts to drag the TARDIS down with it, the Doctor is unable to stop the TARDIS from making a emergency landing.</p>', 7, 21, '1984-01-26', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/46/116990.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324332/doctor-who-21x07-frontios-part-one'),
(324333, 'Frontios, Part Two', 766, '<p>The Doctor works to help the injured colonist, Tegan discovers a file in a closed drawer called "Deaths Unaccountable". Meanwhile, Plantagenate works to convict the Doctor of being the source of the attacks on Frontios.</p>', 8, 21, '1984-01-27', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/46/117105.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324333/doctor-who-21x08-frontios-part-two'),
(324334, 'Frontios, Part Three', 766, '<p>Turlough starts to regain ancestral memories of the Tractators, the Doctor having discovered the Tractators works to discover what their plan is.</p>', 9, 21, '1984-02-02', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/46/117120.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324334/doctor-who-21x09-frontios-part-three'),
(324335, 'Frontios, Part Four', 766, '', 10, 21, '1984-02-03', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/46/117148.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324335/doctor-who-21x10-frontios-part-four'),
(324337, 'Resurrection of the Daleks, Part One', 766, '<p>The Doctor starts having problems navigating the TARDIS through the space-time vortex and ends up on Earth in the future where strange events are going on with imitation police officers and soldiers from the future.</p>', 11, 21, '1984-02-08', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/47/118612.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324337/doctor-who-21x11-resurrection-of-the-daleks-part-one'),
(324338, 'Resurrection of the Daleks, Part Two', 766, '<p>The time mercenaries reveal that they are working for the Daleks and their plan is to release Davros from prison so he can help the Daleks after their loosing their war with the Movelans.</p>', 12, 21, '1984-02-08', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/47/118613.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324338/doctor-who-21x12-resurrection-of-the-daleks-part-two');
INSERT INTO `episode` (`id`, `nom`, `idSerie`, `resume`, `numero`, `saison`, `premiere`, `urlImage`, `url`) VALUES
(324339, 'Resurrection of the Daleks, Part Three', 766, '<p>The Daleks capture the Doctor and plan to duplicate him and his companions as part of their plan to attack the high Council of Gallifrey. Davros starts converting Daleks and their helpers over to his control.</p>', 13, 21, '1984-02-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/47/118687.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324339/doctor-who-21x13-resurrection-of-the-daleks-part-three'),
(324341, 'Resurrection of the Daleks, Part Four', 766, '<p>The Doctor works to foil Davros''s and the Daleks plans. With the help of Tegan, Tourlough and some of the Daleks mental twins, the Daleks are defeated and Davros has a unexpected surprise awaiting him.</p>', 14, 21, '1984-02-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/49/122603.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324341/doctor-who-21x14-resurrection-of-the-daleks-part-four'),
(324342, 'Planet of Fire, Part One', 766, '<p>The Tardis receives a distress signal and at the same time Kamelion seems to be having problems while linked into the Tardis. Following the distress signal the Doctor arrives on Lanzarote and Turlough rescues Peri. Turlough seems to know where the distress signal is coming from.</p>', 15, 21, '1984-02-23', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/52/130500.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324342/doctor-who-21x15-planet-of-fire-part-one'),
(324343, 'Planet of Fire, Part Two', 766, '<p>The Master strengthens his control over Kamelion in order to be able to complete his goals and tries to get Peri under his control.</p>', 16, 21, '1984-02-24', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/52/130505.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324343/doctor-who-21x16-planet-of-fire-part-two'),
(324344, 'Planet of Fire, Part Three', 766, '<p>Turlough is taken to his fathers ship, the Doctor and The Master battle for control of Kamelion so The Master can go through with his plan.</p>', 17, 21, '1984-03-01', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/52/130509.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324344/doctor-who-21x17-planet-of-fire-part-three'),
(324345, 'Planet of Fire, Part Four', 766, '<p>In order to complete his plan to bring himself back to full size after his accident with his tissue compression eliminator, The Master tries to destroy the Doctor. Turlough makes a decision and tells the Doctor why he was exiled to Earth.</p>', 18, 21, '1984-03-02', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/52/130516.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324345/doctor-who-21x18-planet-of-fire-part-four'),
(324346, 'The Caves of Androzani, Part One', 766, '<p>The Doctor lands on one of the twin planets of Androzani where he along with Peri are mistaken for gun runners and sentenced to death.</p>', 19, 21, '1984-03-08', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/52/130531.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324346/doctor-who-21x19-the-caves-of-androzani-part-one'),
(324347, 'The Caves of Androzani, Part Two', 766, '<p>Sharez Jek and his androids save the Doctor and Peri from execution when he rescues them. Then he takes a shine to Peri and wants her with him forever. Later the Doctor and Peri find out they are dying from Spectrox Toxemia, having been poisoned when they handled the Spectrox nest upon first entering the cave system.</p>', 20, 21, '1984-03-09', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/57/143718.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324347/doctor-who-21x20-the-caves-of-androzani-part-two'),
(324348, 'The Caves of Androzani, Part Three', 766, '<p>The Doctor escapes the Mag,a creature and is taken prisoner by the gun runners; The real Salateen takes Peri back to General Challek and is then kidnapped again by Sharaz Jek.</p>', 21, 21, '1984-03-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/57/143807.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324348/doctor-who-21x21-the-caves-of-androzani-part-three'),
(324349, 'The Caves of Androzani, Part Four', 766, '', 22, 21, '1984-03-16', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/57/143887.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324349/doctor-who-21x22-the-caves-of-androzani-part-four'),
(324350, 'The Twin Dilemma, Part One', 766, '<p>The twin human children Romulus and Remus are kidnapped by the mysterious professor Edgeworth. The Children appear to be genius''s. Meanwhile the Doctor seems to be having stability problems with his new regeneration and is acting erratically. </p>', 23, 21, '1984-03-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/64/161816.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324350/doctor-who-21x23-the-twin-dilemma-part-one'),
(324351, 'The Twin Dilemma, Part Two', 766, '<p>The Doctor and Perry arrive at the facility on Titan 3 where Romulus and Remus are being held. The Doctor is taken prisoner by one of the Professors guards. When the Doctor is brought to the professor he recognizes him as Azmael the Master of Jaconda.</p>', 24, 21, '1984-03-23', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/295902.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324351/doctor-who-21x24-the-twin-dilemma-part-two'),
(324353, 'The Twin Dilemma, Part Three', 766, '<p>The Doctor, Peri and Hugo Lang arrive on Jaconda only to discover the massive devastation that the planet has suffered. Azmael is told about the destruction of the Titan 3 outpost.</p>', 25, 21, '1984-03-29', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/295903.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324353/doctor-who-21x25-the-twin-dilemma-part-three'),
(324354, 'The Twin Dilemma, Part Four', 766, '<p>The Doctor attempts to halt Mestor''s true plan for the planet of Jaconda, Azmael has a decision to make for his world.</p>', 26, 21, '1984-03-30', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/295916.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324354/doctor-who-21x26-the-twin-dilemma-part-four'),
(324356, 'Attack of the Cybermen, Part One', 766, '<p>The Doctor and Peri investigate strange signals, in the process, The Tardis lands at the spot where it all began. I.M. Formemans junk yard on Totters Lane. The Doctor is followed by some odd policemen. After landing, he works on the TARDIS''s Chameleon circuit and the TARDIS starts to change shape but seems to have a bit of trouble blending in after such a long time of not working.</p>', 1, 22, '1985-01-05', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/295919.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324356/doctor-who-22x01-attack-of-the-cybermen-part-one'),
(324358, 'Attack of the Cybermen, Part Two', 766, '<p>The Doctor discovers that the Cybermen are involved with the strange distress signal. Peri and the Doctor discover who Lytton is working for and do their best to keep the Cybermen from gaining time travel.</p>', 2, 22, '1985-01-12', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/295933.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324358/doctor-who-22x02-attack-of-the-cybermen-part-two'),
(324360, 'Vengeance on Varos, Part One', 766, '<p>After having power supply problems with the TARDIS, the Doctor and Peri land on the planet Varos where their leaders are punished by the citizens on National television when they are displeased with the leaders actions. The Doctor quickly becomes a fugitive.</p>', 3, 22, '1985-01-19', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/296118.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324360/doctor-who-22x03-vengeance-on-varos-part-one'),
(324361, 'Vengeance on Varos, Part Two', 766, '', 4, 22, '1985-01-26', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/296123.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324361/doctor-who-22x04-vengeance-on-varos-part-two'),
(324363, 'The Mark of the Rani, Part One', 766, '', 5, 22, '1985-02-02', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/116/291193.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324363/doctor-who-22x05-the-mark-of-the-rani-part-one'),
(324364, 'The Mark of the Rani, Part Two', 766, '', 6, 22, '1985-02-09', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/116/291197.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324364/doctor-who-22x06-the-mark-of-the-rani-part-two'),
(324365, 'The Two Doctors, Part One', 766, '', 7, 22, '1985-02-16', NULL, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324365/doctor-who-22x07-the-two-doctors-part-one'),
(324367, 'The Two Doctors, Part Two', 766, '', 8, 22, '1985-02-23', NULL, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324367/doctor-who-22x08-the-two-doctors-part-two'),
(324368, 'The Two Doctors, Part Three', 766, '', 9, 22, '1985-03-02', NULL, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/324368/doctor-who-22x09-the-two-doctors-part-three'),
(325226, 'Timelash, Part One', 766, '<p>The Doctor and Mel are drawn into a Time Corridor and end up on the planet Karfel where the 3rd Doctor once visited. While there he meets a leader who seems to enjoy war and a strange man named Herbert.</p>', 10, 22, '1985-03-09', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/296203.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325226/doctor-who-22x10-timelash-part-one'),
(325229, 'Timelash, Part Two', 766, '<p>The Doctor confronts the Borad and try''s to deal with his plot to take over the world and eradicate human life. Later, the Doctor and Mel find out who Herbert really is.</p>', 11, 22, '1985-03-16', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/296204.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325229/doctor-who-22x11-timelash-part-two'),
(325232, 'Revelation of the Daleks, Part One', 766, '', 12, 22, '1985-03-23', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/296215.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325232/doctor-who-22x12-revelation-of-the-daleks-part-one'),
(325234, 'Revelation of the Daleks, Part Two', 766, '', 13, 22, '1985-03-30', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/296236.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325234/doctor-who-22x13-revelation-of-the-daleks-part-two'),
(325562, 'The Trial of a Time Lord, Part One (The Mysterious Planet)', 766, '<p>The Doctor is taken to a Time Lord space Station and put on trial for his life. The Valeyard uses past examples of the Doctors activities taken from ''The Matrix'', the repository of all Gallifreyan knowledge to show how the Doctor has interfered with other worlds. In this installment of the Trial story Arc, The Doctor''s visit to the planet Ravalox is told and how he interfered with the indigenous population of that world when he saved it from a devastating explosion.</p>', 1, 23, '1986-09-06', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/296255.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325562/doctor-who-23x01-the-trial-of-a-time-lord-part-one-the-mysterious-planet'),
(325563, 'The Trial of a Time Lord, Part Two (The Mysterious Planet)', 766, '<p>The Doctor is saved from the stoning in the nick of time and taken to see the Immortal who wants to use the Doctors far greater knowledge to his advantage. Meanwhile, Peri is taken before Queen Katryca of the local tribe and told that she is to become part of the tribe and take many husbands because there is a shortage of women.</p>', 2, 23, '1986-09-13', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/296497.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325563/doctor-who-23x02-the-trial-of-a-time-lord-part-two-the-mysterious-planet'),
(325564, 'The Trial of a Time Lord, Part Three (The Mysterious Planet)', 766, '<p>The Doctor escapes from the Immortal one and goes to the local tribe, there he is imprisoned along with Glitz and the Immortal one sends a service robot out to retrieve the escaped Time Lord. While the Doctor is imprisoned with Glitz awaiting execution, Glitz informs the Doctor of the true name of the planet.</p>', 3, 23, '1986-09-20', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/296509.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325564/doctor-who-23x03-the-trial-of-a-time-lord-part-three-the-mysterious-planet'),
(325565, 'The Trial of a Time Lord, Part Four (The Mysterious Planet)', 766, '<p>Queen Katryca and the rest of the tribesmen arrive at the underground bunker where they confront Drathro The Immortal one. The Doctor tries to convince Drathro that he will repair the Black Light system while he fears that a possible upcoming explosion of the system could have the potential to destroy the universe.</p>', 4, 23, '1986-09-27', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/296529.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325565/doctor-who-23x04-the-trial-of-a-time-lord-part-four-the-mysterious-planet'),
(325567, 'The Trial of a Time Lord, Part Five (Mindwarp)', 766, '<p>After arguments, the Inquisitor warns both the Doctor and the Valeyard, reminding them that they are in judicial proceedings and to behave. The Valeyard then presents evidence relating to the Doctor landing his TARDIS on the planet Thoros Beta where the Doctor and Peri flee in order to avoid being accused of a crime they did not commit. In the process they arrive at a experimental laboratory where they rescue King Yrcanos.</p>', 5, 23, '1986-10-04', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/296530.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325567/doctor-who-23x05-the-trial-of-a-time-lord-part-five-mindwarp'),
(325568, 'The Trial of a Time Lord, Part Six (Mindwarp)', 766, '<p>As the Valeyard presents events to the Doctor and the Time Lords, the Doctor informs them that he does not remember the events occurring. Peri encounters Matrona who allows her to join Mentor''s servants in order to protect her from the guard. As things progress, the Doctor''s behavior becomes more erratic as he trys to mislead Dr. Crozier.</p>', 6, 23, '1986-10-11', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/296539.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325568/doctor-who-23x06-the-trial-of-a-time-lord-part-six-mindwarp'),
(325569, 'The Trial of a Time Lord, Part Seven (Mindwarp)', 766, '<p>Dr. Crozier prepares to transplant Mentor''s brain with the help of the Doctor, while king Yrcanos, Peri and Dorf prepare to attack the Mentors. In the laboratory, Dr. Crozier decides that Peri may be a compatible body donor and sends for her.</p>', 7, 23, '1986-10-18', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/296542.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325569/doctor-who-23x07-the-trial-of-a-time-lord-part-seven-mindwarp'),
(325570, 'The Trial of a Time Lord, Part Eight (Mindwarp)', 766, '<p>The Doctor works to free king Yrcanos and Dorf. Kiv prepares for his surgical procedure and Peri is strapped down and shaved in preparation, before the Doctor can help her, the Time Lords extract him for the Trial. The Valeyard then presents what happened next from The Matrix files and the Doctor is shocked at what he see''s occur.</p>', 8, 23, '1986-10-25', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/296688.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325570/doctor-who-23x08-the-trial-of-a-time-lord-part-eight-mindwarp'),
(325571, 'The Trial of a Time Lord, Part Nine (Terror of the Vervoids)', 766, '<p>Arriving back in the courtroom, the Doctor starts his defense by showing the future beginning with his arrival onboard the spaceship Hyperion III which is on it''s way from the planet Mogar to Earth with a cargo of rare metals. The Doctor shows the court that the TARDIS picked up a distress signal and he responded to it. Upon arrival, the Doctor tells Mel that he can sense evil. They are then captured and brought before Commodore Travers.</p>', 9, 23, '1986-11-01', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/296556.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325571/doctor-who-23x09-the-trial-of-a-time-lord-part-nine-terror-of-the-vervoids'),
(325572, 'The Trial of a Time Lord, Part Ten (Terror of the Vervoids)', 766, '<p>The crew of the Hyperion discover that the Pods have been opened, The Doctor is brought to the bridge where Commander Travers questions him and Mel about murders and disappearing bodies. The Doctor starts to wonder about Dr. Laskey and decides to investigate her.</p>', 10, 23, '1986-11-08', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/296558.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325572/doctor-who-23x10-the-trial-of-a-time-lord-part-ten-terror-of-the-vervoids'),
(325574, 'The Trial of a Time Lord, Part Eleven (Terror of the Vervoids)', 766, '<p>Mel overhears someone plotting to kill all the animal-king onboard the Hyperion and has taped the conversation, unfortunately the tape vanishes. Meanwhile Bruchner is becoming increasingly worried about the situation in the Hydrophics Centre. It is soon discovered that the creatures that emerged from the pods are Vervoids and they are using the ships air ducts to move around unseen.</p>', 11, 23, '1986-11-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/296564.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325574/doctor-who-23x11-the-trial-of-a-time-lord-part-eleven-terror-of-the-vervoids'),
(325575, 'The Trial of a Time Lord, Part Twelve (Terror of the Vervoids)', 766, '<p>The Vervoids overhear what is planned for them and begin their attempt to prevent it from happening. The ship starts to head towards a black hole and in the attempt to save it, the ship ends up being hijacked adding to the already existing problems. The Doctor then assists the crew in saving their ship and in the process ends up being charged with a more serious charge in the Time Lords trial.</p>', 12, 23, '1986-11-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/296565.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325575/doctor-who-23x12-the-trial-of-a-time-lord-part-twelve-terror-of-the-vervoids'),
(325576, 'The Trial of a Time Lord, Part Thirteen (The Ultimate Foe)', 766, '<p>As the trial of the Doctor continues, an old foe of the Doctor makes an appearance startling the Doctor, the keeper of the Matrix and the Inquisitor alike. The Doctor and the court then discovers who the Valeyard really is. The Doctor goes inside the Matrix after the Valeyard in an attempt to capture him and also prove his innocence in the process.</p>', 13, 23, '1986-11-29', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/119/298266.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325576/doctor-who-23x13-the-trial-of-a-time-lord-part-thirteen-the-ultimate-foe'),
(325578, 'The Trial of a Time Lord, Part Fourteen (The Ultimate Foe)', 766, '<p>The Doctor continues his quest to capture and stop the Valeyard, the Master assists him with the help of Glitz, leaving everyone to wonder if the Master may have plans of his own for the Doctor and the Time Lords. As things progress, in the strange world of the Valeyard the Doctor comes closer to either stopping the Valeyards evil plans or the end of his existence.</p>', 14, 23, '1986-12-06', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/119/298268.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325578/doctor-who-23x14-the-trial-of-a-time-lord-part-fourteen-the-ultimate-foe'),
(325579, 'Time and the Rani, Part One', 766, '<p>The Doctor wakes after regeneration with memory problems, he is helped by Mel who is telling him about his important project that he has been working on but does not remember. Meanwhile, another Mel is assisting one of the inhabitants of the planet after he mistakes her for one of the Rani''s assistants.</p>', 1, 24, '1987-09-07', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/116/291201.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325579/doctor-who-24x01-time-and-the-rani-part-one'),
(325581, 'Time and the Rani, Part Two', 766, '<p>Mel searches for the Doctor and runs into a indigenous life form and has to explain that she is looking for The Doctor who may be able to help his people, meanwhile the Rani works to keep the Doctor convinced that she is Mel so he will help her with her plans.</p>', 2, 24, '1987-09-14', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/119/298556.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325581/doctor-who-24x02-time-and-the-rani-part-two'),
(325582, 'Time and the Rani, Part Three', 766, '<p>The Doctor discovers how the Rani is getting the planets residents to cooperate with her. He then trys to trade a part that the Rani needs for Mel.</p>', 3, 24, '1987-09-21', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/119/298571.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325582/doctor-who-24x03-time-and-the-rani-part-three'),
(325583, 'Time and the Rani, Part Four', 766, '<p>The Doctor gradually starts recovering from his regeneration and begins to piece together the Rani'' plan after finding the real Melanie. He then discovers that the Rani has taken the greatest minds in history and brought them all together to complete the mathematical calculations related to her nefarious plan to take over the universe.</p>', 4, 24, '1987-09-28', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/119/298553.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325583/doctor-who-24x04-time-and-the-rani-part-four'),
(325584, 'Paradise Towers, Part One', 766, '<p>The Doctor lands the Tardis at a fancy hotel called Paradise Towers where Mel is looking forward to having a good time. When they arrive, things are not quite what they were expecting. Right after landing, the Doctor and Mel meet the Red Kangs and find out about their opponents, the Blue Kangs. </p>', 5, 24, '1987-10-05', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/124/312146.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325584/doctor-who-24x05-paradise-towers-part-one'),
(325585, 'Paradise Towers, Part Two', 766, '<p>The Doctor meets with the Red Kangs again and asks them why no one questions all the strange deaths at Paradise Towers.</p>', 6, 24, '1987-10-12', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/125/312788.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325585/doctor-who-24x06-paradise-towers-part-two'),
(325586, 'Paradise Towers, Part Three', 766, '<p>Mel, after having met some very strange ladys, has to work to escape their clutches. Meanwhile the Doctor leans more information about the Great Architect.</p>', 7, 24, '1987-10-19', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/125/312789.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325586/doctor-who-24x07-paradise-towers-part-three'),
(325587, 'Paradise Towers, Part Four', 766, '<p>The Great Architect in his new human body sets out to eliminate all the remaining humans in the Towers. The Doctor has to work with both the Red and Blue Kangs to come up with a plan that will stop his plans in their tracks. Pex has a serious decision to make.</p>', 8, 24, '1987-10-26', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/125/312790.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325587/doctor-who-24x08-paradise-towers-part-four'),
(325588, 'Delta and the Bannermen, Part One', 766, '<p>The Doctor and Mel win a trip to Disneyland in 1959 but after an accident in space, they end up in South Wales instead, along with an assassin and his intended victim...</p>', 9, 24, '1987-11-02', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/183/458263.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325588/doctor-who-24x09-delta-and-the-bannermen-part-one'),
(325589, 'Delta and the Bannermen, Part Two', 766, '<p>Gavrok and the Bannermen have arrived on Earth, searching for Delta. They slaughter the holidaymakers without compunction to draw her out.</p>', 10, 24, '1987-11-09', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/183/458264.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325589/doctor-who-24x10-delta-and-the-bannermen-part-two'),
(325590, 'Delta and the Bannermen, Part Three', 766, '<p>As Billy and Ray do what they can to help save Delta and the baby, the Doctor and Goronwy the beekeeper face Gavrok and his Bannermen one last time...</p>', 11, 24, '1987-11-16', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/183/458265.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325590/doctor-who-24x11-delta-and-the-bannermen-part-three'),
(325592, 'Dragonfire, Part One', 766, '<p>On Iceworld, the Doctor and Mel meet Ace, who has found herself there after a timestorm. While Ace nearly joins Kane''s mercenaries, the Doctor and Glitz explore the ice caverns.</p>', 12, 24, '1987-11-23', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/183/458268.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325592/doctor-who-24x12-dragonfire-part-one'),
(325593, 'Dragonfire, Part Two', 766, '<p>The Doctor and Glitz meet the infamous dragon, which is really a biomechanoid. Meanwhile Kane turns on his allies, as he cannot trust anyone in his search for the dragonfire...</p>', 13, 24, '1987-11-30', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/183/458267.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325593/doctor-who-24x13-dragonfire-part-two'),
(325594, 'Dragonfire, Part Three', 766, '<p>Shown the archive by the biomechanoid, the Doctor discovers that Kane is from the dead world of Proamon. Mel witnesess the destruction of the Nosferatu and Ace faces temptation.</p>', 14, 24, '1987-12-07', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/183/458266.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325594/doctor-who-24x14-dragonfire-part-three'),
(325599, 'Remembrance of the Daleks, Part One', 766, '<p>The Doctor and Ace land on Earth and the Doctor is curious about a parked van with a strange antenna. The Doctor and Ace then go to I.M. Formans junk yard with the military scientists and discover a alien presence. </p>', 1, 25, '1988-10-05', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/162/405157.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325599/doctor-who-25x01-remembrance-of-the-daleks-part-one'),
(325600, 'Remembrance of the Daleks, Part Two', 766, '<p>The Doctor visits a local funeral home to retrieve a coffin shaped device that he calls the ''Hand Of Omega'', meanwhile the Daleks use the transmat device in the basement of Coal Hill School to transport to Earth to search for the ''Hand of Omega''.</p>', 2, 25, '1988-10-12', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/162/405158.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325600/doctor-who-25x02-remembrance-of-the-daleks-part-two'),
(325602, 'Remembrance of the Daleks, Part Three', 766, '<p>The Doctor explains what the ''Hand Of Omega'' is, meanwhile the 2 Dalek factions struggle against each other to obtain the Gallifreyan device. Ace makes a upsetting discovery.</p>', 3, 25, '1988-10-19', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/162/405159.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325602/doctor-who-25x03-remembrance-of-the-daleks-part-three'),
(325604, 'Remembrance of the Daleks, Part Four', 766, '<p>The Doctor has his final encounter with the Daleks involving ''The Hand of Omega''.</p>', 4, 25, '1988-10-26', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/162/405160.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325604/doctor-who-25x04-remembrance-of-the-daleks-part-four'),
(325607, 'The Happiness Patrol, Part One', 766, '<p>The Happiness Patrol walk the streets of Terra Alpha, destroying all the killjoys, on the orders of the despotic Helen A. And in the Kandy Kitchen, something terrible lurks...</p>', 5, 25, '1988-11-02', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/183/458269.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325607/doctor-who-25x05-the-happiness-patrol-part-one'),
(325609, 'The Happiness Patrol, Part Two', 766, '<p>The Doctor escapes the Kandyman while Ace meets the Pipe People. Later, fleeing for her life, she is captured and selected to audition for the Happiness Patrol.</p>', 6, 25, '1988-11-09', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/183/458270.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325609/doctor-who-25x06-the-happiness-patrol-part-two'),
(325612, 'The Happiness Patrol, Part Three', 766, '<p>As the Doctor leads the Pipe People towards reclaiming their world, Helen A faces betrayal from those closest to her and the Kandyman comes to a sticky end.</p>', 7, 25, '1988-11-16', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/183/458271.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325612/doctor-who-25x07-the-happiness-patrol-part-three'),
(325614, 'Silver Nemesis, Part One', 766, '<p>A group of neo-Nazis in South America are seeking the Nemesis Statue – as is a shuttle full of Cybermen and the mysterious Lady Peinforte from the 17th century.</p>', 8, 25, '1988-11-23', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/183/458272.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325614/doctor-who-25x08-silver-nemesis-part-one'),
(325617, 'Silver Nemesis, Part Two', 766, '<p>The Cybermen have the Nemesis Statue but Lady Peinforte and Richard fight back using gold-tipped arrows. Meanwhile, De Flores still has a plan to set in motion.</p>', 9, 25, '1988-11-30', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/183/458273.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325617/doctor-who-25x09-silver-nemesis-part-two'),
(325620, 'Silver Nemesis, Part Three', 766, '<p>The Nemesis Statue is alive, thanks to Lady Peinforte''s insanity, and with De Flores''s Nazis wiped out by the Cybermen, Nemesis claims it has secrets to reveal...</p>', 10, 25, '1988-12-07', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/183/458274.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325620/doctor-who-25x10-silver-nemesis-part-three'),
(325622, 'The Greatest Show in the Galaxy, Part One', 766, '<p>Bellboy and Flowerchild escape the Psychic Circus but are pursued by the Chief Clown. The Doctor and Ace meet other visitors to Segonax, some of whom are not what they seem...</p>', 11, 25, '1988-12-14', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/183/458275.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325622/doctor-who-25x11-the-greatest-show-in-the-galaxy-part-one'),
(325623, 'The Greatest Show in the Galaxy, Part Two', 766, '<p>The mysterious family watching the acts within the ring,dissatisfied with Nord, destroy him. Captain Cook goes to extreme measures to ensure he''s not the next to displease them...</p>', 12, 25, '1988-12-21', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/183/458276.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325623/doctor-who-25x12-the-greatest-show-in-the-galaxy-part-two'),
(325625, 'The Greatest Show in the Galaxy, Part Three', 766, '<p>Ace and Bellboy team up to stop the Chief Clown while the Doctor realises that he is next into the ring. The Captain has another trick up his sleeve and shows Mags''s true colours.</p>', 13, 25, '1988-12-28', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/183/458277.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325625/doctor-who-25x13-the-greatest-show-in-the-galaxy-part-three'),
(325626, 'The Greatest Show in the Galaxy, Part Four', 766, '<p>The Gods of Ragnarok are revealed and while waiting for Ace to escape the Chief Clown, the Doctor must entertain them as long as possible in the dimension of the Dark Circus...</p>', 14, 25, '1989-01-04', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/183/458278.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325626/doctor-who-25x14-the-greatest-show-in-the-galaxy-part-four'),
