(325662, 'Survival, Part Three', 766, '<p>While Ace tries to resist the influence of the Cheetah Planet, the Master tries to leave the planet before it''s too late.<br></p>', 14, 26, '1989-12-06', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/22/56449.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/325662/doctor-who-26x14-survival-part-three'),
(355489, 'Payback', 101, '<p>Jason employs aggressive investigative tactics when he assists Alicia and Lucca with a student loan case. Also, Howard Lyman alleges ageism at Lockhart, Agos &amp; Lee, pointing to Cary as the primary offender, and Eli stirs up Florrick family drama on Peter''s presidential campaign.</p>', 5, 7, '2015-11-01', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/25/63211.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/355489/the-good-wife-7x05-payback'),
(366281, 'Épisode 1', 6131, '', 1, 1, '2015-04-27', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/23/59554.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/366281/le-bureau-des-legendes-1x01-episode-1'),
(377114, 'The War Games, Part Nine', 766, '<p>To prove his loyalty to the Aliens, the Doctor is ordered to reprocess his friends while the Security Chief finally uncovers evidence of the War Chief''s treachery.</p>', 43, 6, '1969-06-14', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281970.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/377114/doctor-who-6x43-the-war-games-part-nine'),
(377115, 'The War Games, Part Ten', 766, '<p>The TARDIS is drawn to the planet of the Time Lords where both the Doctor and the War Lord are placed on trial.</p>', 44, 6, '1969-06-21', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281971.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/377115/doctor-who-6x44-the-war-games-part-ten'),
(390552, 'Lies', 101, '<p>Alicia and Lucca defend a client who was fired from a technology firm for failing a polygraph test. Also, Eli plots to leak something that would damage Peter''s presidential campaign but could inadvertently hurt Alicia.</p>', 6, 7, '2015-11-08', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/29/73107.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/390552/the-good-wife-7x06-lies'),
(401000, 'Driven', 101, '<p>Alicia and Lucca join a case involving an automotive executive represented by Lockhart, Agos &amp; Lee, and an employee represented by Louis Canning, who was involved in a crippling accident while test-driving a car operating in "driverless" mode. Also, when Ruth and Eli pursue Courtney Boalt, a potential campaign contributor, Peter moves back in with Alicia to present a united family image</p>', 7, 7, '2015-11-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/30/76376.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/401000/the-good-wife-7x07-driven'),
