(461929, 'Discovery', 101, '<p>Alicia and Lucca join forces with Louis Canning to defend a Web site accused of racial profiling. Meanwhile, Eli and Ruth worry about the nature of Alicia''s relationship with Jason and how it could impact Peter''s presidential campaign.</p>', 9, 7, '2015-11-29', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/32/82203.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/461929/the-good-wife-7x09-discovery'),
(470535, 'Switch', 618, '<p>Jimmy and Kim''s relationship takes a new turn. Mike decides it''s for the best to sever his affiliation with an unrestrained associate.</p>', 1, 2, '2016-02-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/106356.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/470535/better-call-saul-2x01-switch'),
(478984, 'Back to the Butcher', 1825, '<p>Holden and crew make a deal with an unlikely ally on Tycho Station. Along with his conspiracy theories about Julie Mao, Miller''s obsession with the missing girl intensifies.</p>', 5, 1, '2016-01-05', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/38/95234.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/478984/the-expanse-1x05-back-to-the-butcher'),
(478985, 'Rock Bottom', 1825, '<p>Miller discovers revealing information on a hidden data cube. Holden and crew arrive at Tycho Station, surprised by their host''s hidden agenda.</p>', 6, 1, '2016-01-12', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/38/95281.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/478985/the-expanse-1x06-rock-bottom'),
(478986, 'Critical Mass', 1825, '<p>Miller, Holden and his crew struggle to escape Eros, but they''re trapped when the entire station is put on lockdown. On Earth, Avasarala comes to a stunning realization about the origin of the mystery ships.</p>', 9, 1, '2016-02-02', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/43/108121.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/478986/the-expanse-1x09-critical-mass'),
(478988, 'Windmills', 1825, '<p>Holden and crew realize they''re not alone on the Rocinante and find themselves up against a Martian military blockade. Believing all is lost, Miller finds a new reason to forge ahead. Avasarala visits Holden''s family in Montana.</p>', 7, 1, '2016-01-19', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/40/100529.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/478988/the-expanse-1x07-windmills'),
(478989, 'Salvage', 1825, '<p>The crew of the Rocinante discovers a derelict vessel holding a secret that may destroy humankind. Holden and crew are led to Eros, where they finally cross paths with Miller, only to make a horrifying discovery. On Earth, Avasarala receives devastating news.</p>', 8, 1, '2016-01-26', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/108/270867.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/478989/the-expanse-1x08-salvage'),
(487399, 'KSR', 101, '<p>Alicia and Lucca defend a well-respected surgeon who is accused of plotting to commit a crime. Meanwhile, Ruth schemes to remove Jason from Alicia''s life by trying to persuade Courtney Paige to hire him for business in another state.</p>', 10, 7, '2015-12-13', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/34/87326.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/487399/the-good-wife-7x10-ksr'),
(488566, 'Leviathan Wakes', 1825, '<p>Miller, Holden and his crew fight their way to the Rocinante to escape Eros. On Earth, Avasarala fears for the stability of Earth''s government and her family''s safety.</p>', 10, 1, '2016-02-02', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/43/108123.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/488566/the-expanse-1x10-leviathan-wakes'),
(527849, 'Iowa', 101, '<p>Tensions run high as the entire Florrick family is crammed into Peter''s campaign bus with Eli and Ruth on their way to the Iowa Caucuses. Once there, Peter attempts a high-risk political stunt to gain votes for his presidential bid</p>', 11, 7, '2016-01-10', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/39/97743.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/527849/the-good-wife-7x11-iowa'),
(541919, 'Tracks', 101, '<p>Alicia and Cary join forces to defend a former client facing a multi-million dollar lawsuit over ownership rights to his new music. Also, Alicia''s neighbors are unhappy that her law firm is operating out of her apartment and threaten to evict her.</p>', 12, 7, '2016-01-17', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/40/100463.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/541919/the-good-wife-7x12-tracks'),
(553946, 'Chapter One: The Vanishing of Will Byers', 2993, '<p>A young boy mysteriously disappears, and his panicked mother demands that the police find him. Meanwhile, the boy''s friends conduct their own search, and meet a mysterious girl in the forest.</p>', 1, 1, '2016-07-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/67/168918.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/553946/stranger-things-1x01-chapter-one-the-vanishing-of-will-byers'),
(560813, 'The Red Woman', 82, '<p>Jon Snow is dead. Daenerys meets a strong man. Cersei sees her daughter again.</p>', 1, 6, '2016-04-24', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/56/142371.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/560813/game-of-thrones-6x01-the-red-woman'),
(560924, 'Judged', 101, '<p>Alicia argues against Judge Schakowsky when she learns that a former bond court client was wrongfully imprisoned. Also, Diane assists the student editor of a college newspaper when the school threatens to fire her for writing a politically charged article.</p>', 13, 7, '2016-01-31', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/107423.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/560924/the-good-wife-7x13-judged'),
(570418, 'Monday', 101, '<p>Alicia has trouble adjusting when she returns to work at Lockhart, Agos &amp; Lee with Lucca. Their first case, involving a secret new computer tablet, causes a rift within the firm.</p>', 14, 7, '2016-02-14', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/44/112363.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/570418/the-good-wife-7x14-monday'),
(570419, 'Targets', 101, '<p>Alicia joins a secret panel of attorneys advising the U.S. government on a controversial case. Also, Eli hires Elsbeth Tascioni to uncover why the FBI is targeting Peter.</p>', 15, 7, '2016-02-21', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/46/115034.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/570419/the-good-wife-7x15-targets'),
(570420, 'Hearing', 101, '<p>As the grand jury against Peter Florrick is assembled, with Assistant U.S. Attorney Connor Fox leading the proceedings, Alicia, Eli and Peter''s lawyer, Mike Tascioni, attempt to discover what charges are being leveled against him. Also, Alicia and Jason attempt to spend a quiet weekend together but are interrupted by her meddling family.</p>', 16, 7, '2016-03-06', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/47/119843.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/570420/the-good-wife-7x16-hearing');
INSERT INTO `episode` (`id`, `nom`, `idSerie`, `resume`, `numero`, `saison`, `premiere`, `urlImage`, `url`) VALUES
(578663, 'Chapter Two: The Weirdo on Maple Street', 2993, '<p>While the search for the missing Will continues, Joyce tells Jim about a call she apparently received from her son. Meanwhile, Jane warns Mike that there are bad people after her, and he realizes that she knows what happened to Will.</p>', 2, 1, '2016-07-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/72/181376.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/578663/stranger-things-1x02-chapter-two-the-weirdo-on-maple-street'),
(578664, 'Chapter Three: Holly, Jolly', 2993, '<p>While Nancy looks for a missing Barbara and realizes that Jonathan may have been the last person to see her, Mike and his friends go out with Jane to find the missing Will. Meanwhile, Jim tracks Will to the lab.</p>', 3, 1, '2016-07-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/67/168920.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/578664/stranger-things-1x03-chapter-three-holly-jolly'),
(578665, 'Chapter Four: The Body', 2993, '<p>Jim realizes that the government is covering something up about Will''s death and begins a personal investigation. Meanwhile, Nancy discovers that Jonathan has information about Barbara''s disappearance, while Mike and his friends smuggle Jane into the school so she can use the ham radio to contact Will.</p>', 4, 1, '2016-07-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/67/168921.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/578665/stranger-things-1x04-chapter-four-the-body'),
(578666, 'Chapter Five: The Flea and the Acrobat', 2993, '<p>Jim searches for Will at Hawkins Laboratory, but finds something unexpected. Meanwhile, Lonnie helps Joyce bury Will but reveals an ulterior motive for returning to town, while the boys find a way to locate Will but discover that Jane is opposing them.</p>', 5, 1, '2016-07-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/67/168922.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/578666/stranger-things-1x05-chapter-five-the-flea-and-the-acrobat'),
(578667, 'Chapter Six: The Monster', 2993, '<p>Jonathan manages to pull Nancy back to the real world from the Upside Down. Meanwhile, Lucas refuses to help with the search for Jane and goes to Hawkins Labs on his own, while Dustin and Mike look for the missing girl.</p>', 6, 1, '2016-07-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/67/168923.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/578667/stranger-things-1x06-chapter-six-the-monster'),
(578668, 'Chapter Seven: The Bathtub', 2993, '<p>Jim manages to bring everyone together so that they can join forces to reconnect Jane to the Upside Down and find Will. Meanwhile, the government closes in on Jane and the boys.</p>', 7, 1, '2016-07-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/67/168925.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/578668/stranger-things-1x07-chapter-seven-the-bathtub'),
(578669, 'Chapter Eight: The Upside Down', 2993, '<p>Jim convinces Brenner to let him and Joyce enter the Upside Down to find Will... unaware that Brenner plans to recover Jane no matter what it takes. Meanwhile, Nancy and Jonathan prepare to trap the monster at the Byers house, but receive an unexpected visitor.</p>', 8, 1, '2016-07-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/67/168926.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/578669/stranger-things-1x08-chapter-eight-the-upside-down'),
(603277, 'Cobbler', 618, '<p>Mike brokers a deal in order to keep a potentially messy situation intact; Jimmy tries to exonerate an eccentric client.</p>', 2, 2, '2016-02-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/46/115178.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/603277/better-call-saul-2x02-cobbler'),
(603278, 'Amarillo', 618, '<p>Jimmy''s client outreach efforts succeed, and he exhibits new heights of showmanship; Mike is puzzled by Stacey''s upsetting news.</p>', 3, 2, '2016-02-29', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/47/117636.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/603278/better-call-saul-2x03-amarillo'),
(607710, 'The Human Beast', 12840, '', 1, 1, '2014-09-18', NULL, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/607710/ptit-quinquin-1x01-the-human-beast'),
(607711, 'The Hearth of Evil', 12840, '', 2, 1, '2014-09-18', NULL, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/607711/ptit-quinquin-1x02-the-hearth-of-evil'),
(607712, 'The Devil Incarnate', 12840, '', 3, 1, '2014-09-25', NULL, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/607712/ptit-quinquin-1x03-the-devil-incarnate'),
(607713, 'Allah Akbar', 12840, '', 4, 1, '2014-09-25', NULL, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/607713/ptit-quinquin-1x04-allah-akbar'),
(617860, 'End', 101, '<p>The series reaches its dramatic conclusion.</p>', 22, 7, '2016-05-08', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/57/142770.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/617860/the-good-wife-7x22-end'),
(628774, 'Gloves Off', 618, '<p>Jimmy''s actions unexpectedly create waves for Kim. Meanwhile, Mike cautiously weighs a lucrative proposal that might bring about dire consequences.</p>', 4, 2, '2016-03-07', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/47/119756.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/628774/better-call-saul-2x04-gloves-off'),
(633518, 'Rebecca', 618, '<p>Jimmy becomes frustrated with his restrictive work environment. Meanwhile, Kim pulls out all the stops to dig herself out of a seemingly bottomless hole at HHM.</p>', 5, 2, '2016-03-14', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/48/122138.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/633518/better-call-saul-2x05-rebecca'),
(633789, 'Shoot', 101, '<p>In a defamation suit over a billboard he put up describing a gun store owner as a murderer. Also, a romantic rendezvous between Alicia and Jason is interrupted when Alicia learns that Grace is being accused of plagiarizing her college entrance essay.</p>', 17, 7, '2016-03-20', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/49/124444.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/633789/the-good-wife-7x17-shoot'),
(636926, 'Bali Ha''i', 618, '<p>Jimmy finds comfort in familiarity; Kim receives a life-changing proposal; when he is threatened, Mike finds himself pushed to the limit.</p>', 6, 2, '2016-03-21', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/49/124436.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/636926/better-call-saul-2x06-bali-hai'),
(637936, 'Unmanned', 101, '<p>Alicia and Diane defend the privacy rights of a therapist whose neighbor, represented by attorney Caitlyn D''Arcy, flies a drone over his home office. Also, Assistant U.S. Attorney Connor Fox attempts to use Eli''s daughter, Marissa, as leverage in the case against Peter, and the power struggle at Lockhart, Agos &amp; Lee reaches a boiling point.</p>', 18, 7, '2016-03-27', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/50/127179.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/637936/the-good-wife-7x18-unmanned'),
(645687, 'Inflatable', 618, '<p>Mike''s growing frustration shows when his hand is forced, but with Jimmy''s help, he works to keep the peace. Meanwhile, Jimmy boldly forges a new path forward.</p>', 7, 2, '2016-03-28', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/50/127351.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/645687/better-call-saul-2x07-inflatable'),
(645688, 'Fifi', 618, '<p>Mike is determined to settle the score with a dangerous adversary. An unexpected opportunity to gain a competitive edge falls in Jimmy''s lap.</p>', 8, 2, '2016-04-04', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/51/129601.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/645688/better-call-saul-2x08-fifi'),
(645689, 'Nailed', 618, '<p>Mike takes a methodical approach to his mission. Someone questions Chuck''s capabilities. Jimmy faces a personal dilemma.</p>', 9, 2, '2016-04-11', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/52/131855.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/645689/better-call-saul-2x09-nailed'),
(645691, 'Klick', 618, '<p>Jimmy is forced to make a hard choice. Mike takes matters into his own hands. Hamlin relays shocking news while Chuck''s condition continues to evolve.</p>', 10, 2, '2016-04-18', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/53/134070.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/645691/better-call-saul-2x10-klick'),
(663426, 'Landing', 101, '<p>Alicia and Lucca travel to Toronto to represent NSA Agent Jeff Delinger who was detained by customs officers while attempting to re-enter the United States. Also, Diane grows concerned when her husband, Kurt McVeigh, decides to retire and sell his business to Holly Westfall, a rival business owner, and Peter contemplates an uncertain future when he faces possible arrest.</p>', 19, 7, '2016-04-17', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/53/134251.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/663426/the-good-wife-7x19-landing'),
(663427, 'Party', 101, '<p>Alicia''s night goes from bad to worse when she throws a party to celebrate Howard and Jackie''s upcoming wedding. Also, Eli asks Jason to investigate Peter in preparation for his trial.</p>', 20, 7, '2016-04-24', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/54/136968.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/663427/the-good-wife-7x20-party'),
(663428, 'Verdict', 101, '<p>As Peter''s trial begins, Alicia works desperately to keep her husband from returning to jail. Also, Diane and Lucca move aggressively to expand the law firm, but face serious opposition from David Lee.</p>', 21, 7, '2016-05-01', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/55/138927.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/663428/the-good-wife-7x21-verdict'),
(664672, 'Home', 82, '<p>Bran trains with the Three-Eyed Raven. In King''s Landing, Jaime advises Tommen. Tyrion demands good news, but has to make his own. At Castle Black, the Night''s Watch stands behind Thorne. Ramsay Bolton proposes a plan, and Balon Greyjoy entertains other proposals.</p>', 2, 6, '2016-05-01', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/56/142372.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/664672/game-of-thrones-6x02-home'),
(664673, 'Oathbreaker', 82, '<p>Daenerys meets her future. Bran meets the past. Tommen confronts the High Sparrow. Arya trains to be No One. Varys finds an answer. Ramsay gets a gift.</p>', 3, 6, '2016-05-08', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/56/142370.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/664673/game-of-thrones-6x03-oathbreaker'),
(664674, 'Book of the Stranger', 82, '<p>Tyrion strikes a deal. Jorah and Daario undertake a difficult task. Jaime and Cersei try to improve their situation.</p>', 4, 6, '2016-05-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/56/142273.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/664674/game-of-thrones-6x04-book-of-the-stranger'),
(664675, 'The Door', 82, '<p>Tyrion seeks a strange ally. Bran learns a great deal. Brienne goes on a mission. Arya is given a chance to prove herself.</p>', 5, 6, '2016-05-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/60/150273.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/664675/game-of-thrones-6x05-the-door'),
