(830870, 'eps2.0_unm4sk-pt2.tc', 1871, '<p>angela happy at evil corp. tyrell MIA and joanna has a new bf? wtf? dom leads fbi investigation into five/nine. elliot demands answers from mr. robot.</p>', 2, 2, '2016-07-13', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/67/168564.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/830870/mr-robot-2x02-eps20unm4sk-pt2tc'),
(830871, 'eps2.1_k3rnel-pan1c.ksd', 1871, '<p>Elliot vows to beat Mr. Robot but it ain''t easy, smh. Angela sees behind the scenes at Evil Corp. Sh*t hits fan with fsociety.</p>', 3, 2, '2016-07-20', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/107/268499.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/830871/mr-robot-2x03-eps21k3rnel-pan1cksd'),
(830872, 'eps2.2_init1.asec', 1871, '<p>Elliot friends Ray, who he hopes can help delete Mr. Robot; Dom makes a major discovery; and Darlene questions whether the FBI or Dark Army is the bigger threat.</p>', 4, 2, '2016-07-27', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/107/268493.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/830872/mr-robot-2x04-eps22init1asec'),
(830873, 'eps2.3_logic-b0mb.hc', 1871, '<p>Elliot can''t quit the game; Dom and the FBI head to China to investigate 5/9; Joanna is haunted; and Darlene calls on Angela for help.</p>', 5, 2, '2016-08-03', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/107/268475.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/830873/mr-robot-2x05-eps23logic-b0mbhc'),
(830874, 'eps2.4_m4ster-s1ave.aes', 1871, '<p>Mr. Robot tries to show Elliot that he can be useful; and Darlene and Angela''s plan doesn''t go as hoped.</p>', 6, 2, '2016-08-10', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/70/176488.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/830874/mr-robot-2x06-eps24m4ster-s1aveaes'),
(830875, 'eps2.5_h4ndshake.sme', 1871, '<p>Mr. Robot and Elliot try to make nice; and Joanna is given an ultimatum.</p>', 7, 2, '2016-08-17', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/71/178952.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/830875/mr-robot-2x07-eps25h4ndshakesme'),
(830876, 'eps2.6_succ3ss0r.p12', 1871, '<p>A video is released by fsociety; Darlene decides to act on an old desire.</p>', 8, 2, '2016-08-24', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/107/268442.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/830876/mr-robot-2x08-eps26succ3ss0rp12'),
(830877, 'eps2.7_init5.fve', 1871, '<p>Angela wants more from E Corp than they want to give; and Elliot and Darlene seek answers.</p>', 9, 2, '2016-08-31', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/73/182686.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/830877/mr-robot-2x09-eps27init5fve'),
(830878, 'eps2.8_h1dden-pr0cess.axx', 1871, '<p>Elliot wonders if Mr. Robot has been lying to him; Darlene attempts to do the right thing; Dom and the FBI get closer.</p>', 10, 2, '2016-09-07', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/73/184601.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/830878/mr-robot-2x10-eps28h1dden-pr0cessaxx'),
(861461, 'eps2.9_pyth0n-pt1.p7z', 1871, '<p>Angela makes an unexpected acquaintance. Elliot does the same. Dom engages in an interesting ama.</p>', 11, 2, '2016-09-14', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/107/268408.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/861461/mr-robot-2x11-eps29pyth0n-pt1p7z'),
(869671, 'The Original', 1371, '<p>A woman named Dolores is a free spirit in the Old West... and unaware that she''s actually an android, programmed to entertain rich guests seeking to act out their fantasies in an idealized vision of the 1880s. However, the people in charge soon realize that their androids are acting in ways that they didn''t anticipate.</p>', 1, 1, '2016-10-02', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/78/195475.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/869671/westworld-1x01-the-original'),
(872189, 'BoJack Kills', 184, '<p>BoJack is framed for the murder of a Whale World dancer. Mr. Peanutbutter and Todd get into a stinky situation with the skunk next door.</p>', 3, 3, '2016-07-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/126/317380.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/872189/bojack-horseman-3x03-bojack-kills'),
(872190, 'Fish Out of Water', 184, '<p>BoJack takes an underwater trip to the Pacific Ocean Film Festival for the "Secretariat" premiere, where he tries to reach out to Kelsey.</p>', 4, 3, '2016-07-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/126/317381.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/872190/bojack-horseman-3x04-fish-out-of-water'),
(872191, 'Love and/or Marriage', 184, '<p>While Todd and BoJack crash a rehearsal dinner, Diane gets high with a client. Princess Carolyn goes on a series of blind dates.</p>', 5, 3, '2016-07-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/126/317382.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/872191/bojack-horseman-3x05-love-andor-marriage'),
(872192, 'Brrap Brrap Pew Pew', 184, '<p>Diane''s tweet lands Sextina Aquafina in hot water. Prankster and A-list actor Jurj Clooners gets under BoJack''s skin.</p>', 6, 3, '2016-07-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/126/317383.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/872192/bojack-horseman-3x06-brrap-brrap-pew-pew'),
(872193, 'Stop the Presses', 184, '<p>Todd builds a giant papier-mâché Todd head. A customer service rep gives BoJack some sound advice when he tries to cancel his newspaper subscription.</p>', 7, 3, '2016-07-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/126/317384.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/872193/bojack-horseman-3x07-stop-the-presses'),
(872194, 'Old Acquaintance', 184, '<p>Bojack is up for a part in David Pincher''s latest film. Diane meets Mr. Peanutbutter''s brother and Todd takes the business in a new direction.</p>', 8, 3, '2016-07-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/126/317385.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/872194/bojack-horseman-3x08-old-acquaintance'),
(872195, 'It''s You', 184, '<p>Mr. Peanutbutter announces the Oscar nominees. BoJack surrounds himself with admirers, but his real friendships are falling apart.</p>', 10, 3, '2016-07-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/126/317387.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/872195/bojack-horseman-3x10-its-you'),
(872196, 'That''s Too Much, Man!', 184, '<p>On a drug-fueled bender, BoJack and Sarah Lynn crash an AA meeting, and BoJack decides to make amends to the people he hurt.</p>', 11, 3, '2016-07-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/126/317388.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/872196/bojack-horseman-3x11-thats-too-much-man'),
(872197, 'That Went Well', 184, '<p>Mr. Peanutbutter saves the day. Todd gets exciting news. BoJack, Diane and Princess Carolyn pursue new opportunities.</p>', 12, 3, '2016-07-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/126/317389.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/872197/bojack-horseman-3x12-that-went-well'),
(872198, 'Best Thing That Ever Happened', 184, '<p>BoJack meets Princess Carolyn at Elefante, leading to a night of soul-searching as they help the staff impress a food critic.</p>', 9, 3, '2016-07-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/126/317386.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/872198/bojack-horseman-3x09-best-thing-that-ever-happened'),
(872199, 'The BoJack Horseman Show', 184, '<p>In 2007, Princess Carolyn finds a new project for BoJack, Diane meets Mr. Peanutbutter at the coffee shop where she works, and Todd kisses a girl.</p>', 2, 3, '2016-07-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/126/317379.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/872199/bojack-horseman-3x02-the-bojack-horseman-show'),
(878469, 'San Junipero', 305, '<p>A woman named Yorkie arrives in the 1987 town of San Junipero, and soon links up with the free-spirited Kelly. But San Junipero isn''t all that it seems...</p>', 4, 3, '2016-10-21', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/79/199563.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/878469/black-mirror-3x04-san-junipero'),
(878470, 'Shut Up and Dance', 305, '<p>Hackers get a compromising video of a teenager, Kenny, and force him and their other blackmail victims to complete an elaborate and increasingly dangerous series of tasks.</p>', 3, 3, '2016-10-21', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/79/199569.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/878470/black-mirror-3x03-shut-up-and-dance'),
(878471, 'Nosedive', 305, '<p>In the near future, everyone is obsessed with getting ratings from others... and a woman, Lacie, is determined to get a high enough rating to buy the home she''s always dreamed of.</p>', 1, 3, '2016-10-21', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/81/203812.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/878471/black-mirror-3x01-nosedive'),
(878472, 'Men Against Fire', 305, '<p>A soldier, Stripe, serves in Europe hunting down mutated humans known as "Roaches." However, he soon discovers that the creatures aren''t what they appear.</p>', 5, 3, '2016-10-21', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/83/208577.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/878472/black-mirror-3x05-men-against-fire'),
(878473, 'Hated in the Nation', 305, '<p>A DIC and her new shadow investigate a reporter''s death and discover that she was the most hated woman in the UK by popular vote... and the vote killed her.</p>', 6, 3, '2016-10-21', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/79/199570.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/878473/black-mirror-3x06-hated-in-the-nation'),
(878474, 'Playtest', 305, '<p>An American, Cooper, leaves the States to avoid facing his mother after the death of his father. Trying to raise money, he signs up to playtest a new VR game for a cutting-edge company and gets more than he expected.</p>', 2, 3, '2016-10-21', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/79/199565.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/878474/black-mirror-3x02-playtest'),
(892064, 'The Vulcan Hello', 7480, '<p>While patrolling Federation space, the U.S.S. Shenzhou encounters an object of unknown origin, putting First Officer Michael Burnham to her greatest test yet.</p>', 1, 1, '2017-09-24', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/128/322025.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/892064/star-trek-discovery-1x01-the-vulcan-hello'),
(909340, 'Chapter One: MADMAX', 2993, '<p>One year after the events with the Upside Down and the Demogorgon, Will meets with a government doctor. The boys discover that there''s a new player in town, and Jim pays a visit to El.</p>', 1, 2, '2017-10-27', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/132/331976.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/909340/stranger-things-2x01-chapter-one-madmax'),
(909342, 'Chapter Two: Trick or Treat, Freak', 2993, '<p>The boys go trick-or-treating on Halloween, and Will has another vision. Meanwhile, El relieves the days following her escape from the Upside Down, and Dustin finds something in the garbage can.</p>', 2, 2, '2017-10-27', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/132/332034.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/909342/stranger-things-2x02-chapter-two-trick-or-treat-freak'),
(909343, 'Chapter Three: The Pollywog', 2993, '<p>Dustin takes in a stray and calls it D''Artagnan. However, his plans to show it to Mr. Clarke don''t go as intended. Meanwhile, Max tries to convince Mike to let her join the group, El sneaks out to pay her friends a visit, and Will decides to take a stand and face his fears.</p>', 3, 2, '2017-10-27', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/132/332039.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/909343/stranger-things-2x03-chapter-three-the-pollywog'),
(909344, 'Chapter Four: Will the Wise', 2993, '<p>After his encounter with the shadow creature, Will''s condition worsens. Meanwhile, Jim and El fight after Jim discovers that El disobeyed the rules, and Owens brings Nancy and Jonathan to Hawkins Labs for a chat.</p>', 4, 2, '2017-10-27', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/132/332045.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/909344/stranger-things-2x04-chapter-four-will-the-wise'),
(909345, 'Chapter Five: Dig Dug', 2993, '<p>Jim is trapped in the Upside Down, and Joyce enlists Bob to help find him. Meanwhile, Nancy and Jonathan go to Murray, and El learns about the circumstances surrounding her birth.</p>', 5, 2, '2017-10-27', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/132/332050.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/909345/stranger-things-2x05-chapter-five-dig-dug'),
(909346, 'Chapter Six: The Spy', 2993, '<p>Owens and his team try to find a way to end the shadow creature''s influence on Will. Meanwhile, Dustin and Lucas find unlikely allies in their quest to find Dart.</p>', 6, 2, '2017-10-27', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/132/332052.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/909346/stranger-things-2x06-chapter-six-the-spy'),
(909347, 'Chapter Seven: The Lost Sister', 2993, '<p>El travels to Chicago to find her sister Eight, aka Kali, who has teamed up with other outcasts to kill the men who tormented her at Hawkins Labs.</p>', 7, 2, '2017-10-27', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/132/332055.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/909347/stranger-things-2x07-chapter-seven-the-lost-sister'),
(909348, 'Chapter Eight: The Mind Flayer', 2993, '<p>When the demo-dogs overrun Hawkins Labs, one of the group saves the others at the cost of their own life. When the others get back to the Byers house, they realize what they''re facing and try to get answers from a captive Will.</p>', 8, 2, '2017-10-27', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/132/332059.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/909348/stranger-things-2x08-chapter-eight-the-mind-flayer'),
(909349, 'Chapter Nine: The Gate', 2993, '<p>The group splits up to close the gate, evict the Mind Flayer from Will, and drive the demo-dogs away from Hawkins Lab.</p>', 9, 2, '2017-10-27', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/132/332064.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/909349/stranger-things-2x09-chapter-nine-the-gate'),
(910146, 'eps2.9_pyth0n-pt2.p7z', 1871, '<p>Darlene realizes she is in too deep; an old friend reveals everything to Elliot.</p>', 12, 2, '2016-09-21', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/76/190198.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/910146/mr-robot-2x12-eps29pyth0n-pt2p7z'),
(911201, 'Chestnut', 1371, '<p>Bernard suspects that someone is sabotaging the hosts. Meanwhile, the Man continues his search for the deeper game, and Maeve finds herself in a world of hurt... literally.</p>', 2, 1, '2016-10-09', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/78/195436.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/911201/westworld-1x02-chestnut'),
(911204, 'The Stray', 1371, '<p>Bernard continues to investigate Dolores'' supposed malfunction, and realizes that he has something unexpected on his hands. Meanwhile, Robert talks about the early days of the park, and Teddy receives a new role and narrative.</p>', 3, 1, '2016-10-16', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/79/198183.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/911204/westworld-1x03-the-stray'),
(911205, 'Dissonance Theory', 1371, '<p>While Dolores joins William and Logan on their adventure, the Man in Black continues his search for the entrance to the Maze and meets Armistice. Meanwhile, Robert reveals some of his true power to Theresa and advises her to stay out of his way.</p>', 4, 1, '2016-10-23', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/80/201367.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/911205/westworld-1x04-dissonance-theory'),
(927174, 'Contrapasso', 1371, '<p>Dolores takes the first step on her path of discovery by deciding to write a new story for herself... where she isn''t the damsel. Meanwhile, Elise discovers the Woodcutter''s secret, and Robert pays the Man a visit.</p>', 5, 1, '2016-10-30', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/81/204265.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/927174/westworld-1x05-contrapasso'),
(932057, 'The Adversary', 1371, '<p>While Maeve convinces Felix to show her "upstairs," Teddy and the Man close in on the maze. Meanwhile, Bernard and Elsie close in on the identity of the person who is stealing secrets from the park, while Lee meets with a Delos executive director.</p>', 6, 1, '2016-11-06', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/82/207324.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/932057/westworld-1x06-the-adversary'),
(937256, 'Dragonstone', 82, '<p>Jon organizes the defense of the North. Cersei tries to even the odds. Daenerys comes home.</p>', 1, 7, '2017-07-16', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/120/302038.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/937256/game-of-thrones-7x01-dragonstone'),
(938404, 'Trompe L''Oeil', 1371, '<p>While William and Dolores travel to the unclaimed territories, Charlotte and Theresa make plans to force Robert out of the park using Clementine. Meanwhile, Maeve continues her plans to escape Westworld.</p>', 7, 1, '2016-11-13', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/83/209400.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/938404/westworld-1x07-trompe-loeil'),
(943065, 'Trace Decay', 1371, '<p>Bernard tries to cope with what he did under Robert''s orders. Meanwhile, William and Dolores find a town, and Maeve remembers more of her past. Meanwhile, the Man reveals his past to Teddy.</p>', 8, 1, '2016-11-20', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/84/211554.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/943065/westworld-1x08-trace-decay'),
(943066, 'The Well-Tempered Clavier', 1371, '<p>Bernard forces Robert to take him back into his own memories, while the Man meets with Charlotte. Meanwhile, Dolores escapes the Confederado camp and William gives Logan new orders.</p>', 9, 1, '2016-11-27', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/85/213932.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/943066/westworld-1x09-the-well-tempered-clavier'),
(943067, 'The Bicameral Mind', 1371, '<p>Delores finds out the truth about William''s fate. Meanwhile, Maeve organizes an escape plan, only to discover that someone else is pulling the strings. And Robert plays the final piece in his grand narrative.</p>', 10, 1, '2016-12-04', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/86/216453.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/943067/westworld-1x10-the-bicameral-mind'),
(946020, 'Safe', 1825, '<p>James Holden and the crew deal with the aftermath of their escape from Eros. Martian Marine Gunnery Sergeant Bobbie Draper and her platoon witness the growing tension between Earth and Mars.</p>', 1, 2, '2017-02-01', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/95/239354.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/946020/the-expanse-2x01-safe'),
(1001711, 'The Pilot', 210, '<p>A young woman, Bill, listens to the lectures of a long-time university professor, the Doctor. He soon agrees to tutor her, and Bill realizes that the Doctor is much more than he seems. Bill''s mind is opened to a universe that is bigger and more exciting than she could imagine.</p>', 1, 10, '2017-04-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/106/266867.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1001711/doctor-who-10x01-the-pilot'),
(1008862, 'Inauguration', 18206, '<p>After a financial scam destorys the reputation of lawyer Maia Rindell, while wiping out her mentor and godmother, Diane Lockhart''s, savings; Maia and Diane join one of Chicago''s preeminent law firms.</p>', 1, 1, '2017-02-19', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/99/248194.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1008862/the-good-fight-1x01-inauguration'),
(1010481, 'Doors & Corners', 1825, '<p>With the help of Fred Johnson and the OPA, Miller, Holden and the crew stage a dangerous raid in search of information about the protomolecule. On Earth, Avasarala learns a truth about Fred Johnson.</p>', 2, 2, '2017-02-01', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/96/240426.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1010481/the-expanse-2x02-doors-corners'),
(1041746, 'Mabel', 618, '<p>Jimmy and Chuck''s relationship deteriorates; Kim feels the pressure of running her own firm; Mike investigates the note left on his car.</p>', 1, 3, '2017-04-10', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/106/266601.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1041746/better-call-saul-3x01-mabel'),
(1046600, 'Static', 1825, '<p>Holden and Miller butt heads about how the raid was handled.</p>', 3, 2, '2017-02-08', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/97/243170.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1046600/the-expanse-2x03-static'),
(1046601, 'Godspeed', 1825, '<p>Miller devises a dangerous plan to eradicate what''s left of the protomolecule on Eros.</p>', 4, 2, '2017-02-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/96/240323.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1046601/the-expanse-2x04-godspeed'),
(1046602, 'Home', 1825, '<p>The Rocinante chases an asteroid as it hurtles toward Earth.</p>', 5, 2, '2017-02-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/99/249160.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1046602/the-expanse-2x05-home'),
(1049332, 'Paradigm Shift', 1825, '<p>Earth and Mars search for answers in the aftermath of the asteroid collision. A dangerous new threat emerges outside Jupiter, while one lie threatens to destroy the Rocinante crew.</p>', 6, 2, '2017-03-01', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/100/251140.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1049332/the-expanse-2x06-paradigm-shift'),
(1049333, 'The Seventh Man', 1825, '<p>Preparations for the Earth/Mars peace conference tighten the tension on Erringwright.</p>', 7, 2, '2017-03-08', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/101/253453.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1049333/the-expanse-2x07-the-seventh-man'),
(1049334, 'Pyre', 1825, '<p>Naomi tracks down signs of the protomolecule; Fred Johnson''s control over the OPA collapses.</p>', 8, 2, '2017-03-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/102/255816.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1049334/the-expanse-2x08-pyre'),
(1049336, 'Cascade', 1825, '<p>Holden leads his crew through the war-torn station on Ganymede.</p>', 10, 2, '2017-03-29', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/107/268568.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1049336/the-expanse-2x10-cascade'),
(1049337, 'Here There Be Dragons', 1825, '<p>Bobbie makes a decision that changes her life forever.</p>', 11, 2, '2017-04-05', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/105/264089.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1049337/the-expanse-2x11-here-there-be-dragons'),
(1049338, 'The Monster and the Rocket', 1825, '<p>A discovery pushes Naomi and Holden apart and sets the Roci crew against each other.</p>', 12, 2, '2017-04-12', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/106/267273.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1049338/the-expanse-2x12-the-monster-and-the-rocket'),
(1049339, 'Caliban''s War', 1825, '<p>The Roci crew must fight to save the ship.</p>', 13, 2, '2017-04-19', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/107/269762.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1049339/the-expanse-2x13-calibans-war'),
(1051911, 'Witness', 618, '<p>Jimmy and Kim hire an assistant; Mike seeks out a mysterious acquaintance; Chuck uses the law to gain an advantage over Jimmy.</p>', 2, 3, '2017-04-17', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/106/266442.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1051911/better-call-saul-3x02-witness'),
(1051912, 'Sunk Costs', 618, '<p>Jimmy decides to represent a new client to Kim''s dismay; Mike meets a formidable ally who gives a tempting offer.</p>', 3, 3, '2017-04-24', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/108/271802.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1051912/better-call-saul-3x03-sunk-costs'),
(1051913, 'Sabrosito', 618, '<p>Jimmy asks a favor of Mike; new complications disrupt Salamancas'' business; Chuck and Jimmy struggle with a compromise.</p><p></p>', 4, 3, '2017-05-01', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/110/275271.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1051913/better-call-saul-3x04-sabrosito'),
(1051914, 'Chicanery', 618, '<p>Kim and Jimmy face off with an adversary; Jimmy looks to Chuck''s past to secure his future; Jimmy loses an ally and gains another.</p>', 5, 3, '2017-05-08', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/111/277578.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1051914/better-call-saul-3x05-chicanery'),
(1051915, 'Off Brand', 618, '<p>Jimmy has a new endeavor; Chuck pushes himself to the limit; Nacho finds himself in a power struggle.</p>', 6, 3, '2017-05-15', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/280392.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1051915/better-call-saul-3x06-off-brand'),
(1051916, 'Expenses', 618, '<p>Jimmy tries to settle debts; Nacho reunites with an acquaintance; Mike helps Stacey with a project and makes a connection.</p>', 7, 3, '2017-05-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/113/283183.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1051916/better-call-saul-3x07-expenses'),
(1060429, 'Smile', 210, '<p>For her first proper trip, the Doctor takes Bill to a colony in the future. They discover that the skeleton crew has been wiped out, and a terrible fate awaits the awakening colonists unless they do something.</p>', 2, 10, '2017-04-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/108/270590.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1060429/doctor-who-10x02-smile'),
(1060430, 'Thin Ice', 210, '<p>The Doctor takes Bill to the Great Frost Fair on the Thames in 1814... and they discover that something is living beneath the ice. Something huge, and hungry.</p>', 3, 10, '2017-04-29', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/109/273543.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1060430/doctor-who-10x03-thin-ice'),
(1060431, 'Knock Knock', 210, '<p>Bill and her mates receive an offer to move into an old house at a price they can''t refuse. However, they soon discover that the price is much higher than promised.</p>', 4, 10, '2017-05-06', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/110/276666.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1060431/doctor-who-10x04-knock-knock'),
(1060432, 'Oxygen', 210, '<p>The Doctor takes Bill and Nardole to a space station in the future in response to a distress call. They discover that 36 of the 40 crew members are dead... but their suits aren''t.</p>', 5, 10, '2017-05-13', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/110/276889.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1060432/doctor-who-10x05-oxygen'),
(1060433, 'Extremis', 210, '<p>The Pope asks the Doctor to investigate the mysteries of <i>Veritas</i>, a book that has caused everyone to read it to commit suicide. However, the Doctor soon learns that <i>Veritas </i>contains the real history of the universe… and it is enough to drive anyone to suicide.</p>', 6, 10, '2017-05-20', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/111/279409.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1060433/doctor-who-10x06-extremis'),
(1060434, 'The Pyramid at the End of the World', 210, '<p>The Monks materialize a 5,000-year-old pyramid as a threat, and then demand the consent of Earth''s leaders to save the planet from imminent destruction.</p>', 7, 10, '2017-05-27', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285038.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1060434/doctor-who-10x07-the-pyramid-at-the-end-of-the-world'),
(1060435, 'The Lie of the Land', 210, '<p>Bill finds herself in a world that is ruled by the Monks, and has always believed that the Monks have been there to guide humanity and defend it. Worse, the Doctor is working with the Monks to solidify their rule.</p>', 8, 10, '2017-06-03', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285141.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1060435/doctor-who-10x08-the-lie-of-the-land'),
(1060436, 'Empress of Mars', 210, '<p>The Doctor and Bill end up stranded on Mars investigating how a 19th century message appeared on the 21st century Mars. They find Victorian soldiers... invading an ancient Ice Warrior hive.</p>', 9, 10, '2017-06-10', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/116/290534.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1060436/doctor-who-10x09-empress-of-mars'),
(1060437, 'The Eaters of Light', 210, '<p>The Doctor, Bill, and Nardole travel to Scotland in the distant past to learn what happened to the Ninth Legion. They soon discover an alien creature stalking the woods, and the gate that must remain guarded no matter what.</p>', 10, 10, '2017-06-17', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/117/292590.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1060437/doctor-who-10x10-the-eaters-of-light'),
(1060438, 'World Enough and Time', 210, '<p>The Doctor decides to test Missy''s reformation with a mission to investigate a distress signal coming from a 400-mile-long ship near a black hole. However, things soon take a turn for the worst and an old friend returns with new allies.</p>', 11, 10, '2017-06-24', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/117/292594.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1060438/doctor-who-10x11-world-enough-and-time'),
(1060439, 'The Doctor Falls', 210, '<p>The Doctor rescues Bill, but warns her that there''s no going back to the way things were. Meanwhile, the Cybermen prepare to invade another floor of the spaceship, and Missy must choose sides.</p>', 12, 10, '2017-07-01', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/118/297407.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1060439/doctor-who-10x12-the-doctor-falls'),
(1066324, 'First Week', 18206, '<p>Diane raises eyebrows while settling in as a new partner at Reddick, Boseman &amp; Kolstad. Maia continues to deal with the repercussions of her family''s Ponzi scheme. Lucca and Maia unexpectedly pick up a new case.</p>', 2, 1, '2017-02-19', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/99/248193.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1066324/the-good-fight-1x02-first-week'),
(1073966, 'The Schtup List', 18206, '<p>Adrian and Barbara face a cruel realization about a high profile client. While second chair to Diane on a case, Lucca is in for more than she bargained for thanks to the state''s attorney''s office''s golden boy, Colin Morello. Maia visits her father in prison.</p>', 3, 1, '2017-02-26', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/100/250114.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1073966/the-good-fight-1x03-the-schtup-list'),
(1079148, 'The Weeping Somnambulist', 1825, '<p>Bobbie becomes a political pawn in the struggle between Earth and Mars.</p>', 9, 2, '2017-03-22', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/103/258546.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1079148/the-expanse-2x09-the-weeping-somnambulist'),
(1079892, 'The Law of Vacant Places', 32, '<p>A petty sibling rivalry between two brothers escalates and brings chaos to a small Minnesotan community.</p>', 1, 3, '2017-04-19', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/107/269783.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1079892/fargo-3x01-the-law-of-vacant-places'),
(1084613, 'Henceforth Known as Property', 18206, '<p>Diane and Lucca represent an ovarian cancer survivor looking to obtain custody of her previously donated embryos. Maia is the victim of a fake social media account. Mike Kresteva pays a visit to Reddick, Boseman &amp; Kolstad.</p>', 4, 1, '2017-03-05', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/101/254662.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1084613/the-good-fight-1x04-henceforth-known-as-property'),
(1091165, 'Stoppable: Requiem for an Airdate', 18206, '<p>Lucca defends a TV writer-producer in a copyright infringement case with ties to the President of the United States. Mike Kresteva takes aim at Reddick, Boseman &amp; Kolstad.</p>', 5, 1, '2017-03-12', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/101/254664.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1091165/the-good-fight-1x05-stoppable-requiem-for-an-airdate'),
