(1561475, 'Kerblam!', 210, '<p>After receiving an anonymous request for help, the Doctor and her companions travel to a moon of Kandoka to investigate the universe''s large retailer: Kerblam.</p>', 7, 11, '2018-11-18', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/174/435078.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1561475/doctor-who-11x07-kerblam'),
(1561477, 'The Witchfinders', 210, '<p>The Doctor and her companions materialize in 17th century England and soon find themselves embroiled in local witchcraft... which is the prelude to an alien invasion.</p>', 8, 11, '2018-11-25', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/175/438569.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1561477/doctor-who-11x08-the-witchfinders'),
(1561479, 'It Takes You Away', 210, '<p>The TARDIS group materialize in Norway in 2018, and soon find themselves involved with a blind girl and her missing father.</p>', 9, 11, '2018-12-02', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/174/437071.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1561479/doctor-who-11x09-it-takes-you-away'),
(1561480, 'The Battle of Ranskoor Av Kolos', 210, '<p>The Doctor and her companions respond to nine separate distress signals all originating from the same planet: Ranskoor Av Kolos. There they discover a stranded ship, an amnesiac pilot... and an old foe.</p>', 10, 11, '2018-12-09', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/174/437070.jpg', 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1561480/doctor-who-11x10-the-battle-of-ranskoor-av-kolos'),
